    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>下垂 口袋</strong> 是一款建立在台球基础上的战略 Roguelike 游戏。</h2>周五晚上，你出城时发现自己身处一家台球酒吧。来自各行各业的人们都已做好准备，等待您的挑战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>前所未有的台球</strong></h2>下垂 口袋 不仅仅是台球，还有很多其他功能。从保龄球到 20 面骰子，每个特殊球都有其独特的机制，可以帮助或阻碍您的胜利之路。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/a47b3bea21b96815c9d8a97a4777773a.poster.avif?t=1759951522\" width=622 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/a47b3bea21b96815c9d8a97a4777773a.webm?t=1759951522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>水中的鲨鱼</strong></h2>台球鲨鱼在每轮比赛结束时都会等待，准备通过在牌桌上应用新规则来缩短您的比赛时间。通过改变物理、增加障碍或仅仅用球填满桌子，老板都会要求你尽最大努力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/4d39488e8019eb9311fd7d384ff5d16a.poster.avif?t=1759951522\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/4d39488e8019eb9311fd7d384ff5d16a.webm?t=1759951522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/4d39488e8019eb9311fd7d384ff5d16a.mp4?t=1759951522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小饰品和小玩意s</strong></h2>累积您的积分并通过物品和升级快速致富。将数十种粉笔、架子和台球杆组合起来，形成数百种潜在的组合，并在 下垂 口袋 中尽情享受成功的乐趣！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/f958754971a084294b34303d2abafa54.poster.avif?t=1759951522\" width=590 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005620/extras/f958754971a084294b34303d2abafa54.webm?t=1759951522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
